# pipenv
#   According to pypa/pipenv#1191, it is recommended to not commit Pipfile.lock if it is a deployment.
#   For a library, it should be committed, but for an app, it depends.
# Pipfile.lock

# poetry
#   Similar to Pipfile.lock, it is generally recommended to include poetry.lock in version control.
#   However, for applications, it's often preferred to keep it.
